MonkeyType Enhancer is an extension to monkeytype.com that automates typing sessions and targets weak points to speed up the process of increasing your typing speed and accuracy.

MonkeyType Enhancer tracks many stats including your session wpm, accuracy, and accuracy for each letter so that your training can be customized to what you need most.
